Job Details
Leading chains of bakeshop in UAE is now on expansion. Urgently looking for Supervisors - Retail shop and production area. Immediate employment will be provided as well as other benefits as per UAE labor law. Kindly submit your employment profile with latest photo and expected salary at  easywayuae@yahoo.com
Requirements
Experience in people handling of different nationalities, managing shifts, inceasing sales & customer service is a must. Good command of English is required. Ability to speak Arabic and other languages, is an advantage.
